  <body>
  <div>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_emergency_care_place_of_injury__snomed_ct_">EMERGENCY CARE PLACE OF INJURY (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is the same as attribute 
              <xref outputclass="attribute" keyref="attribute_clinical_terminology_code">CLINICAL TERMINOLOGY CODE</xref>.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="element"
               keyref="element_emergency_care_place_of_injury__snomed_ct_">EMERGENCY CARE PLACE OF INJURY (SNOMED CT)</xref>
 is the 
              <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct">SNOMED CT</xref>
® concept ID which is used to identify the type of 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_location">LOCATION</xref>
 at which the 
              <xref outputclass="class" keyref="class_patient">PATIENT</xref>
 was present when the injury occurred.        </p>
      <p>
         <xref outputclass="supportingInformation"
               keyref="supporting_definition_snomed_ct_refset">SNOMED CT Refset</xref>
 Metadata:        </p>
